text: Laraesima densepunctata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1950. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Laraesima densepunctata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1950
